message.body: Hey! I have a bod meeting until 6:30pm. I thought I could skip out but can't. Where are you going to be before you head to the airport?
Just finished dinner, chillin out a bit before I get on the plane. Could get a quick dessert/beer/whatever, or see you next time!
I'm sorry, I'll see you next time! I'm so glad I got to see you for a little bit. You look great and really happy. Come back soon!
Definitely. You look great and happy too! Soooooo how was your date last night?
Fabulous. I kinda like him but I wanna take it suuuuuuper slow.
Awesome, I like it! Keep me posted...
Will do. And you do the same! Safe travels!
